the bulgarian businessmen checking into the 
europejski hotel shook their heads in disbelief when they saw the 
redandwhite lettered sign saying solidarity press office hotel 
club 1st floor 
a bellhop sensing the concern of his guests over the prospect of 
ordering a drink in a room occupied by polands leading opposition 
