organizer of the press office 
dozens of union activists have pitched in to run the press 
service compiling news bulletins and monitoring official coverage 
of the talks 
every afternoon solidarity press aides redecorate the 
rosecolored room a solidarity banner is hung on the wall and piles 
of stillbanned underground newspapers are placed on a coffee table 
