authorities attempts to quash it and since the roundtable talks 
began its press corps has turned out in force for the flurry of 
solidarity and official news conferences 
the addition of these alternative journalists and questions 
from curious solidarity activists who clog the room often cause the 
news conferences to drag on for as long as two hours sending some 
western journalists to the bar or back to their offices 
from time to time its difficult for us some solidarity 
