from the hospital because he was mistakenly ruled insane by a judge 
in 1957 
on wednesday district judge pat brian ordered murphy transferred 
to opportunity house on the edge of the hospital property he will 
be allowed to come and go during the day but must report back each 
night 
this deals with the most complex and social problems this court 
or any other district court has ever resolved the judge said 
the judge ruled that in addition to wearing the electronic 
monitoring device murphy must return to court every four months for 
review 
