round trips at 99 each between any two domestic destinations served 
by northwest airlines in the 48 contiguous states 
in addition they will get vouchers for reduced rates on 
northwest to specific destinations and bonus mileage toward 
northwests free travel program 
tickets must be purchased with an american express card issued to 
the student named on the voucher 
american express also plans to publish a quarterly lifestyle 
magazine american express connections that will be sent to its 
college student cardholders the magazine will offer tips on travel 
and money management stories about campus theater and the 
professions and mailorder clothing electronics entertainment and 
travel 
american express officials declined to specify how much it was 
spending on the program but said it was a multimillion dollar 
effort 
